title: Not getting able to see scene viewer in Google search
content: So I'm a pixel 3a user,for the past couple of days when I search for animals there appears an option to view it in 3d . I used to get it work earlier,but for the past couple of days I'm not able to view it.Tried different solutions like clearing of cache,rebooting,uninstalling updates but no results.So is there any solution?
